    "  └─ Thumbnails" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "  └─ Thumbnails"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Minimized\" view mode gives you an overview of your entire year. Additional sharing is available in this view mode to share your entire year." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“精简” 视图模式可纵览你的全年数据。该模式支持分享全年记录的额外分享功能。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Normal\" view mode gives you a more focused view with 7 days per row representing the 7 days of a week. Layout is shifted to match the weekday." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“常规” 视图模式聚焦展示每周数据，每行显示一周 7 天。布局会按星期几自动适配。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Saved to iCloud\" is disabled in system settings. To enable sync, go to:\n\nSettings → [Your Name] → iCloud → Saved to iCloud → Joodle\n\nand turn on the toggle." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "系统设置中“保存到 iCloud”已停用。要启用同步，请前往：\n\n设置 → [你的名字] → iCloud → 保存到 iCloud → Joodle\n\n并开启开关。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"Saved to iCloud\" is disabled. Enable it in Settings → [Your Name] → iCloud → Saved to iCloud → Joodle." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "系统设置中“保存到 iCloud”已停用。请前往设置 → [你的名字] → iCloud → 保存到 iCloud → Joodle 开启。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
